bilingual.source: People celebrate to show that they are grateful for the year's supply of food.
bilingual.target: 人们庆祝以表示他们对一年的食物供应感激。
他们的食物供应非常微薄。

bilingual.source: Supply is insufficient to meet the demand.
We need to increase the supply of food.
bilingual.target: 我们需要增加食品的供应。
为了确保供应，我们必须优先购买。

bilingual.source: They had a problem with their water supply.
bilingual.target: 他们的水供应出现了问题。

bilingual.source: The gas supply in this area is very stable.

bilingual.source: State Grid provides a stable power supply.

list.abstract: Supply（英[səˈplaɪ]，美[səˈplaɪ]），英语单词，作动词为供应；提供。作名词为供应量。作副词为柔软地；易弯地。短语搭配有water supply（供水）。例句为“Wood supply was plentiful in Romania.（罗马尼亚木材供应充足。）” Supply名词类近义词有provision等，动词类有afford、tender等，相关反义词有demand、recall。

yingyinNormal.en: You'd get power and plumbing from the supply at King's Barrow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 金斯巴罗农场能为我们供应水电。

yingyinNormal.en: She's shut down three of our supply centers for human subjects in the last two months.
yingyinNormal.zh: 过去两个月里她已经破坏了我们三个人体试验品的供应中心

yingyinNormal.en: This tiny inlet of Hainan Island is the key to one of China's biggest supply problems: their love of seafood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 海南岛的这一小小港湾就有解决中国最棘手的供应难题之一——他们对海鲜的热爱——的关键。

yingyinNormal.en: Soon, they'll control the energy supply of half the world. In effect, they become a new superpower. The world needs Robert Fischer to change his mind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很快非榭能源公司会控制半个世界的能源供应，最终非榭能源公司会成为大赢家。总言之要令费舍尔改变想法。

yingyinNormal.en: On the other hand, if the money supply remains the same, while more goods and services are produced, each dollar's value would increase in a process known as deflation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 另一方面，如果货币供应量不变，但商品和服务增加，每一分钱的价值就会增加，这过程就叫通货紧缩。

yingyinNormal.en: On the other hand, if the money supply remains the same, while more goods and services are produced, each dollar's value would increase in a process known as deflation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 另一方面，如果货币供应量不变，但商品和服务增加，每一分钱的价值就会增加，这过程就叫通货紧缩。

yingyinNormal.en: While companies like Honda, Toyota, BMW, and Nissan have opened new factories, spawning a vast network of American-owned auto-supply firms, all these dots you see here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而像本田，丰田，宝马和日产却开了新的工厂，为美产汽车供应公司铺开了巨网，你在这里见到的这些点。

yingyinNormal.en: So you don't care about the owners, just about food supply.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么，你们并不在乎庄园主们，只担心粮食生产。

yingyinNormal.en: It's safe with the Vision. These days safe is in short supply.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它在幻视手里是安全的，如今安全也是一种奢侈了。

yingyinNormal.en: And each one needs fuel so it can supply power 365 days a year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个电站都要消耗能量，所以才能1年365天不间断供电。

yingyinNormal.en: Supply lines here. While the Eastern Sea hems them in both south and east.
yingyinNormal.zh: 补给线在这里，同时在东部海岸的从南部和东部包围他们。

yingyinNormal.en: For example, I noticed that you purchase your tampons one-month supply at a time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如说我发现你的卫生巾一次是购买一个月的量。

yingyinNormal.en: When the price of something rises, people will supply more of it and buy less of it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当某种东西的价格上升，人们自然会增加生产，然后买的人就会变少。

yingyinNormal.en: Uganda, 2012. Synthetic Cathinone. You put it in the water supply of a guerrilla army base.
yingyinNormal.zh: 2012年，乌干达。合成卡西酮 。被用于污染了陆军基地的供给水源。

yingyinNormal.en: Just to play devil's advocate, maybe he has the most basic understanding of supply and demand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我忠言逆耳一下，或许他对基本的供需关系有所了解呢。

yingyinNormal.en: You supply a service. Yes. Traditionally, higher education is a product marketed only to the elite.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是在提供服务。是的，传统意义上，高等教育是一项只为精英人群服务的产品。

yingyinNormal.en: He poisoned the water supply, bringing on the dark ages. Death and disease and suffering ran rampant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他在水源下了毒，带来了黑暗时期，死亡，疾病，肆意猖獗。

yingyinNormal.en: Time being something of which we don't have an infinite supply, so if we could be about our business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 时间并不是取之不尽用之不竭的。麻烦让我们继续工作吧。

yingyinNormal.en: When Sheldon showers second, any and all measures shall be taken to ensure an adequate supply of hot water.
yingyinNormal.zh: "当谢尔顿第二个洗澡时必须采取各种方法保证有足够的热水"。

yingyinNormal.en: Ben. Did you know about the push-button phone working with the landline? The supply box? Tactical radio channels?
yingyinNormal.zh: 本，你知道按键式电话能和陆线连接起来用吗？电源箱？火灾指挥用频道？

examination_example.sentence: Then there's the fact that large American companies are much more globalized than ever before, with <highlight>supply</highlight> chains spread across a larger number of countries.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 还有一个事实是，美国大公司比以往任何时候都更加全球化，供应链遍布更多的国家。

examination_example.sentence: Scientists need journals in which to publish their research, so they will <highlight>supply</highlight> the articles without monetary reward.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科学家们需要期刊来发表他们的研究，所以他们会在没有金钱回报的情况下提供文章。

examination_example.sentence: Humans overwhelmingly live in valleys, and on <highlight>supplies</highlight> of fresh water.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 绝大多数人类生活在山谷中，依靠淡水供应。

examination_example.sentence: Court, school, organizations of amateurs, and the traveling actors were all rivals in <highlight>supplying</highlight> a widespread desire for dramatic entertainment.

word_usage.usage:
表示“提供”
supply尤指长时间地定期供应所需或想要之物，不可接双宾语，多用于 supply sb with sth 和 supply sth to sb 结构中。
provide指为某人提供需要或有用的东西，多用于 provide sth for sb 和provide sb with sth 结构中。
afford多指提供抽象的东西，可后接双宾语。
offer指主动给予帮助等，对方可以接受也可以拒绝。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: make something needed or wanted available to someone

examination_example.sentence: That is about 30% of the yearly food <highlight>supply</highlight> (供应) .
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这大约是每年食物供应的30%。

examination_example.sentence: With a limited housing <highlight>supply</highlight>, the average house prices have risen sharply by over 93 percent between 2010 and 2014.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 由于住房供应有限，2010年至2014年期间，平均房价急剧上升了93%以上。

examination_example.sentence: The power <highlight>supply</highlight> on this instrument had failed, so it could no longer be used.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这台仪器的电源出现了故障，因此无法再使用。

examination_example.sentence: And Van Gogh himself would often trade his paintings for food or art <highlight>supplies</highlight> (美术用品) when he was younger.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 而梵高本人在年轻时也经常用他的画作换取食物或美术用品。

examination_example.sentence: I am greatly thankful to you all for sending me food and <highlight>supplies</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我非常感谢你们给我送来食物和物资。

examination_example.sentence: The volunteers deliver food or other <highlight>supplies</highlight> for the elderly in town.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 志愿者们为城里的老年人运送食物或其他用品。
